room_title: Escape room "The Chamber" by Breakin’ The Code in Houma
review: First time I played at breaking the code and we enjoyed it so much we played 3 more games that day.  We couldn't get enough.

room_title: Escape room "The Chamber" by Breakin’ The Code in Houma
review: Very difficult room but we loved every minute of it!  One of the most immersive rooms we have ever played

room_title: Escape room "The Chamber" by Breakin’ The Code in Houma

room_title: Escape room "The Chamber" by Breakin’ The Code in Houma
review: Survived being kidnapped the first time but kidnapper was definitely tricky with his set up in the chamber

room_title: Escape room "The Chamber" by Breakin’ The Code in Houma

review: This was the secone game the kids played as part of their birthday,  they had a great time!

room_title: Escape room "The Chamber" by Breakin’ The Code in Houma
review: Breaking the code and taking names.   Great value and a great time

room_title: Escape room "The Chamber" by Breakin’ The Code in Houma
review: Very good room, if you are looking for a challenge this room is the best to try.   I will be back to attempt it again

room_title: Escape room "The Chamber" by Breakin’ The Code in Houma
review: Took the family back to Breakin the Code and as always we had a great time! Their puzzles are all original ideas unlike some places and the staff is great!  We will be back again.

room_title: Escape room "The Chamber" by Breakin’ The Code in Houma
review: Our float, Kajun Kerizma came attempt the Chamber last night. We had a blast. We haven't conquered the mission yet, which means we WILL be back. The staff was professional and we can't wait for next time.
